<html>

<head>
    <title>Swaad Recipe</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/about.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="nav-container
            <% if(showRoutes == true) {%>
                increase-height
                <%}%>
            ">
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <div class="logo">Swaad Recipe</div>
                <form class="nav-routes" action="/about" method="post">
                    <button class="route-button">
                        <img class="hamburger" src="/Images/hamburger.png" alt="">
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-route-buttons 
                <% if(showRoutes == true) {%>
                    show-route-buttons
                    <%}%>
                    ">
                <div class="home-route">
                    <form action="/home" method="post" class="routes">
                        <button class="route-button">Home</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="recipes-route">
                    <form action="/recipes" method="post" class="routes">
                        <button class="route-button">Recipes</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="about-route">
                    <form action="/about" method="post" class="routes">
                        <button class="route-button">About</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main-body">
            At Swaad Recipe, we believe that cooking is not just a necessity, but a form of art. Our platform is
            dedicated to providing a space where food enthusiasts can come together to share their passion for cooking
            and discover new and exciting recipes.

            Our website features a wide variety of recipes from all over the world, contributed by talented cooks who
            are passionate about their craft. From traditional family recipes passed down through generations to
            innovative and creative dishes, there's something for everyone on Swaad Recipe.

            In addition to browsing and sharing recipes, we also offer a range of resources to help you become a better
            cook. Our blog features articles on cooking techniques, ingredient guides, and recipe roundups, while our
            community forum is a great place to ask questions and get advice from fellow food lovers.

            But Swaad Recipe is more than just a website - it's a community. We encourage our users to connect with each
            other, share their experiences, and build friendships through their love of food. Whether you're looking for
            inspiration, guidance, or just a friendly chat, you'll find it here.

            If you have any questions or comments about Swaad Recipe, we'd love to hear from you. You can contact us via
            email at info@swaadrecipe.com or through our social media channels. We're always happy to hear feedback and
            suggestions from our users.

            Thank you for choosing Swaad Recipe as your go-to source for delicious recipes and culinary inspiration. We
            hope you enjoy exploring our website and becoming part of our community.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>